'''Bebidja''' is an area of [[Chad]]. It has large [[oil reserves]] and has such been of interest to foreign oil companies such as [[ExxonMobil]], [[Royal Dutch Shell|Shell]] and [[Elf Aquitaine|Elf]].<ref>Rosenblum, P. (2000) 'Pipeline Politics in Chad', Current History, p. 197</ref>

